data.description: NO HOA! BIG 283sf 5th BR on main floor (not included in the hsf #'s) with closet (has it’s own Jen-Air a/c-heating unit) that’s perfect for a game room, MIL-suite. In Ground Pool! 1 YR Warranty. PREMIUM private 1.34 acre cul-de-sac lot w/fenced yard, shaded areas around the pool, separate shop/garage, shady natural areas. Inside you’ll notice brand new LVP flooring downstairs, New matching carpet upstairs, a sunny kitchen w/SS appliances, double-wide pantry, granite countertops, undermount sink, ALL appliances are included (w/d/fridge/stove/microwave/dw). DR currently being used as an office. HVAC system serviced annually, kitchen appliances are new. This home is located right near too many restaurants to count, the Speedway, Super Target, Publix, schools, I-85. So much to do out here within minutes. Bring your RV/boat/jet ski’s/toys with you - save $ on storage fees. Just an all around pretty home with lots of SPACE! Needs some minor updates, nothing major. $10,000 Seller Credit!
